msgctxt "176_Man"
msgid "The guest of honor tonight is Kazuma Kiryu. I'm afraid that I cannot escort you without him."
msgstr "El invitado de honor esta noche es Kazuma Kiryu. Me temo que no puedo acompañarte sin el."

msgctxt "236_Man"
msgid "Now then, is everybody ready to depart?"
msgstr "Ahora, ¿está todo el mundo preparado para salir?"

msgctxt "248_Kiryu"
msgid "Yes."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "260_Akiyama"
msgid "Let's be on our way then?"
msgstr "¿Nos vamos entonces?"

msgctxt "272_Saejima"
msgid "You bet."
msgstr "You bet."

msgctxt "284_Tanimura"
msgid "Let's go."
msgstr "Let's go."

msgctxt "308_Kiryu"
msgid "I need to take care of something first."
msgstr "Tengo que ocuparme de algo antes."

msgctxt "320_Akiyama"
msgid "Whoops, looks like I forgot something, too. I'll just go and grab it."
msgstr "Vaya, parece que olvidé algo. Iré a agarrarlo."

msgctxt "344_Saejima"
msgid "I'm gonna go get warmed up."
msgstr "Voy a calentar."

msgctxt "368_Tanimura"
msgid "I should get ready, too."
msgstr "Debería prepararme también."

msgctxt "392_Man"
msgid "Very well. Just let me know when you're ready. I'll be waiting here until dawn."
msgstr "Muy bien. Hazmelo saber cuando estés listo. Esperaré aquí hasta el amanecer."

msgctxt "428_Man"
msgid "Ah, Kiryu-san. I've heard quite a bit about you. Please, allow me to be your guide."
msgstr "Ah, Kiryu-san. He oído hablar bastante de tí. Por favor, déjame ser tu guía."

msgctxt "440_Kiryu"
msgid "All right..."
msgstr "Claro..."

msgctxt "452_Tanimura"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr "Kiryu-san."

msgctxt "476_Kiryu"
msgid "Tanimura?"
msgstr "¿Tanimura?"

msgctxt "488_Saejima"
msgid "We're goin' with ya."
msgstr "Vamos contigo."

msgctxt "500_Akiyama"
msgid "You can't just run off like that, Kiryu. Four of them, one of you? Not exactly sporting odds."
msgstr "No puedes huir así como así, Kiryu. Ellos son cuatro y tú solo uno. No es muy justo que digamos."

msgctxt "512_Tanimura"
msgid "Heh. Sorry, Kiryu. I read the letter. Thought the whole thing sounded a little fishy."
msgstr "Je. Perdón, Kiryu. Leí la carta. Pensé que todo eso era un poco sospechoso."

msgctxt "524_Tanimura"
msgid "You should stop trying to handle everything alone."
msgstr "Deberías dejar de intentar solucionar todo tú solo."

msgctxt "536_Kiryu"
msgid "Guys..."
msgstr "Chicos..."

msgctxt "548_Akiyama"
msgid "They're ruthless killers, and there are four of them. We'd hate to miss the chance to risk life and limb, you know?"
msgstr "They're ruthless killers, and there are four of them. We'd hate to miss the chance to risk life and limb, you know?"

msgctxt "560_Tanimura"
msgid "We don't want you dying out there. Let us help you on this one, Kiryu."
msgstr "No queremos que te mueras ahí fuera. Déjanos ayudarte en esta, Kiryu."

msgctxt "572_Saejima"
msgid "Sounds like you and this Jo Amon guy go way back. We can each take on one of the other three for ya."
msgstr "Parece que ese Amon Jo tiene algo personal contigo. Déjanos encargarnos de los otros tres, uno por uno."

msgctxt "584_Saejima"
msgid "How's that suit you?"
msgstr "¿Qué te parece?"

msgctxt "596_Kiryu"
msgid "All right, if you're sure. I owe you guys."
msgstr "De acuerdo, si estáis seguros. Os lo debo."

msgctxt "608_Kiryu"
msgid "I have to be clear on one thing, though. These guys are real monsters."
msgstr "Sin embargo, tengo que dejar clara una cosa. Estos tipos son verdaderos monstruos."

msgctxt "620_Kiryu"
msgid "We have to all win our fights and come back in one piece. Otherwise, it'll all be for nothing."
msgstr "Todos tenemos que ganar nuestras peleas y volver de una sola pieza. De lo contrario, todo habrá sido en vano."

msgctxt "632_Kiryu"
msgid "But even if we do win, there's no guarantee they won't just come after us again. You could all end up being their targets. Are you really sure about this?"
msgstr "Pero incluso si ganamos, no es seguro de que no vendrán a por nosotros de nuevo. Podríais acabar siendo sus objetivos. ¿Estáis realmente seguros de esto?"

msgctxt "644_Saejima"
msgid "You bet yer ass we are."
msgstr "Puedes apostar tu culo a que sí."

msgctxt "656_Kiryu"
msgid "Okay. I probably won't be able to help you in the middle of battle, so you should all get everything you'll need before we go."
msgstr "Vale. Probablemente no podré ayudaros en medio de la batalla, así que deberíais conseguir todo lo que necesitéis antes de ir."

msgctxt "668_Akiyama"
msgid "Got it."
msgstr "Entiendo."

msgctxt "680_Saejima"
msgid "Sounds good."
msgstr "Me parece bien."

msgctxt "692_Tanimura"
msgid "Understood."
msgstr "Entendido..."

msgctxt "704_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, you heard 'em. Hope you don't mind if I bring some friends to the party."
msgstr "Bueno, ya los habéis oído. Espero que no os importe si traigo a unos amigos a la fiesta."

msgctxt "716_Man"
msgid "Heh, as you wish. By all means, bring a whole army if you like."
msgstr "Je, como quieras. Trae un ejército entero si quieres."

msgctxt "728_Man"
msgid "Now then, is everybody ready to depart?"
msgstr "Ahora, ¿está todo el mundo preparado para salir?"

msgctxt "740_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "752_Akiyama"
msgid "Let's be on our way then?"
msgstr "¿Nos vamos entonces?"

msgctxt "764_Saejima"
msgid "You bet."
msgstr "You bet."

msgctxt "776_Tanimura"
msgid "Let's go."
msgstr "Let's go."

msgctxt "800_Kiryu"
msgid "I need to take care of something first."
msgstr "Tengo que ocuparme de algo antes."

msgctxt "812_Akiyama"
msgid "Whoops, looks like I forgot something, too. I'll just go and grab it."
msgstr "Vaya, parece que olvidé algo. Iré a agarrarlo."

msgctxt "836_Saejima"
msgid "I'm gonna go get warmed up."
msgstr "Voy a calentar."

msgctxt "860_Tanimura"
msgid "I should get ready, too."
msgstr "Debería prepararme también."

msgctxt "884_Man"
msgid "Very well. Just let me know when you're ready. I'll be waiting here until dawn."
msgstr "Muy bien. Hazmelo saber cuando estés listo. Esperaré aquí hasta el amanecer."

msgctxt "896_Man"
msgid "Go to the Arena"
msgstr "Ve a la Arena"

msgctxt "908_Man"
msgid "I need to prepare some more."
msgstr "Necesito prepararme un poco más."

